  "text": "The modes of the high-temperature abrasive wear, depending on oxide properties, are extended comparing to [CITATION_1] , taking into account the situations when sample can loose mass during the corrosion test accompanied with ultrasonic cleaning due to insufficient adhesion (Fig. 1) .",
